com.magnet.android.mms.async.tag

Interface Tag

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoLocationTag, NetworkTag, RequestTimeTag

    public interface Tag
    This interface provides a dynamic tag evaluated by an asynchronous call. It also defines a set of tags that developer can explicitly specify. The name and value of a tag are added to the call when it is invoked or sent to the server.
